1
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,159
Hello again,

2
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:02,840
Mr. Chur.

3
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:03,759
Have a seat.

4
00:01:05,079 --> 00:01:06,680
Your last lecture was well received.

5
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:08,640
I'm discussing another collaboration with the school.

6
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,359
Yes, I attended it.

7
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,159
Your presentation was excellent.

8
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,120
I know.

9
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,159
Seeing you here

10
00:01:16,519 --> 00:01:17,799
actually surprised me.

11
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,239
You didn't even attend

12
00:01:20,239 --> 00:01:21,640
the lecture at Zhangyi College

13
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,760
for its centennial celebration.

14
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,680
I'm surprised you'd come to our school,

15
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:29,079
which is just an ordinary high school.

16
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:31,519
Because of you.

17
00:01:33,480 --> 00:01:34,280
Me?

18
00:01:37,040 --> 00:01:37,879
Just kidding.

19
00:01:38,959 --> 00:01:39,680
Actually,

20
00:01:40,079 --> 00:01:41,200
I'm not a fan of those

21
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:41,959
academic kids.

22
00:01:42,599 --> 00:01:44,599
They think they are special,

23
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,879
but they are just imitating

24
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:46,840
and parroting.

25
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:49,319
They have no potential.

26
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:52,439
Instead of wasting time on them,

27
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,959
I'd rather find some gold in ordinary people.

28
00:01:56,799 --> 00:01:58,560
If I can find a talented one,

29
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:01,400
I can have the blessing

30
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,239
of being an enlightening teacher.

31
00:02:05,879 --> 00:02:07,920
You don't talk like an artist.

32
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:10,840
You came to my lecture.

33
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,080
Do you like these?

34
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:12,759
Yes.

35
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:14,560
I like photography.

36
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,000
With a father like Jiang Changfa,

37
00:02:17,560 --> 00:02:19,560
it shouldn't be hard for you to achieve something.

38
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,520
He's not my father.

39
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,840
My father died a year ago.

40
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:28,719
Jiang Chang...

41
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:32,800
Mr. Jiang is my stepfather.

42
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:36,080
I call him uncle.

43
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:38,479
You don't like him?

44
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,280
You have the right to dislike him.

45
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,360
No one can ask you

46
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,280
to like a man

47
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,680
who suddenly enters your life.

48
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,000
No matter

49
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,639
what role he plays

50
00:02:54,639 --> 00:02:55,680
in your future life.

51
00:02:57,039 --> 00:02:57,319
Yeah.

52
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:04,960
What about your brother?

53
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,199
His name is

54
00:03:07,199 --> 00:03:07,680
Jiang Yue.

55
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:08,560
Yes.

56
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,199
We are not familiar with each other.

57
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:14,319
But he

58
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,879
should be a very good person.

59
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:52,479
If you want it, carve it yourself.

60
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:06,240
A person's talent

61
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:08,240
is not forced out by countdown.

62
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,600
It's really well painted.

63
00:05:24,639 --> 00:05:25,199
I think so.

64
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:28,000
It's going to rain outside.

65
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:29,279
Let me take you home.

66
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:30,480
No, thanks.

67
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,040
I'll take a taxi.

68
00:05:43,160 --> 00:05:43,800
Is your home far?

69
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,480
Not really.

70
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:46,720
Let's go.

71
00:05:51,879 --> 00:05:52,720
Mr. Chu

72
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,720
I think your soul is light.

73
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,120
I envy you.

74
00:05:57,079 --> 00:05:58,720
It's the first time I've heard that description.

75
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:02,519
You don't care about external evaluations and opinions.

76
00:06:02,959 --> 00:06:05,319
You don't blindly worship the concept of public recognition.

77
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,360
and just focus on your own feelings.

78
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,720
Why do I feel like you're scolding me?

79
00:06:12,639 --> 00:06:13,240
No.

80
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,480
I really want to be like you.

81
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,319
Light.

82
00:06:18,399 --> 00:06:20,199
What? Are you heavy?

83
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:21,839
Yes.

84
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,399
Very heavy.

85
00:06:24,639 --> 00:06:26,959
Sometimes I can't even breathe.

86
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,160
Lu Qi.

87
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:36,639
Let me help you.

88
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:05,000
Do you feel better now?

89
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,879
A bit.

90
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,199
How about now?

91
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,920
Still feel heavy?

92
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,639
Much better.

93
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,040
Speak.

94
00:07:47,879 --> 00:07:48,240
Young Master,

95
00:07:48,879 --> 00:07:49,800
the Chu Mo you're looking for

96
00:07:49,839 --> 00:07:50,920
is the son of Chu Tianxiang.

97
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,120
Chu Tianxiang?

98
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,279
Yes.

99
00:07:54,759 --> 00:07:56,639
The great artist who has cooperated with the group.

100
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,639
But unlike him,

101
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:00,120
Zhu Mo doesn't like to show up in public

102
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,279
or accept any interviews.

103
00:08:01,839 --> 00:08:03,079
Except for holding an occasional exhibition.

104
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:03,879
He has always been a mystery.

105
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:05,000
Keep investigating.

106
00:08:05,279 --> 00:08:06,519
Notify me as soon as you have any news.

107
00:08:07,079 --> 00:08:07,759
Yes, young master.

108
00:08:30,759 --> 00:08:31,439
Jiang Yue.

109
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:32,600
Mr. Jiang,

110
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,159
we meet again.

111
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,559
You like getting wet, just do it yourself.

112
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:37,879
Come home with me.

113
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:38,799
Jiang Yue,

114
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,960
didn't I tell you to wait for me?

115
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,440
Did I ask you to follow me?

116
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,279
I can come back by myself.

117
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,080
You came back by yourself?

118
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:25,159
Did you come back by yourself?

119
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:25,639
Chumo,

120
00:09:25,960 --> 00:09:26,639
I told you

121
00:09:26,639 --> 00:09:27,240
not to get too close to him.

122
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,080
Why are you yelling at me?

123
00:09:28,159 --> 00:09:28,519
I...

124
00:09:32,320 --> 00:09:33,200
I'm afraid you'll catch a cold.

125
00:09:34,879 --> 00:09:35,519
The backpack

126
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:40,840
and the clothes,

127
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,759
for a sister who came halfway,

128
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:59,000
isn't your reaction too intense?

129
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:02,679
The vice president of 3Z Group

130
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,600
is willing to be a bodyguard.

131
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,720
Jiang Yue,

132
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,440
you're really good at

133
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,240
maintaining your reputation.

134
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,240
Young Master,

135
00:10:57,799 --> 00:10:59,320
the biological mother of Chu Mo is not Mrs. Chu.

136
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,639
He is the illegitimate son of Chu Tianxiang and Lin Yu.

137
00:11:02,279 --> 00:11:03,480
To cover up the scandal,

138
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:05,559
Chu Mo was sent abroad when he was very young.

139
00:11:06,279 --> 00:11:07,360
Lin Yu was a model,

140
00:11:07,559 --> 00:11:09,039
She was sentenced to 12 years in prison for fraud.

141
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,159
She's still in prison.

142
00:11:11,759 --> 00:11:12,480
And then?

143
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,799
He went to the art academy for further study.

144
00:11:15,440 --> 00:11:16,759
People say he's talented.

145
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,120
He's won many awards at home and abroad.

146
00:11:20,919 --> 00:11:22,159
Besides these,

147
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,759
I haven't found anything else

148
00:11:23,759 --> 00:11:24,519
suspicious for now.
